# Navigation (Expo Router v3)

Source of truth: @ai/rules/projects/fin-app-mobile/architecture.md

## Quick Rules

- Typed routes: `router.push('/wallets')` — no raw string concat
- `useLocalSearchParams<{ id: string }>()` for route params
- `<Link href="/wallets">` for declarative navigation
- Do NOT import from `expo-router` in `shared/`, `entities/`, `features/` — only in `app/` route files and feature screens
- Stack options inside screen: `<Stack.Screen options={{ title: '...' }} />`
- Modal screens: `presentation: 'modal'`
- Deep links: `"scheme": "finapp"` in `app.json`; test via `rtk npx uri-scheme open finapp://wallets --ios`
- Auth guard in root `_layout.tsx` with `useSegments` + `useRouter` — never in individual screens
- Extract ALL `Platform.select` to `src/shared/lib/platform.ts`
